		<h1><small><strong>Welcome to Bright Sparqe</strong></small></h1>
		<a class="subtitle" id="main-subtitle">Bright Sparqe raises money to help homeless people in Australia.</a>
		<div class="content">
			<div class="content_left">
				<%= image_tag("homeless.jpg", :alt => "homeless")%>
			</div>
			<div class="content_right">
				<p>Bright Sparqe's primary objective is to assist and provide one breakfast bag to each homeless men, woman and child. Bright Sparqe will commence the concept in the Melbourne CBD prior to rolling it out nationally. The Organisational Board has agreed, approved and signed-off the approach to supply approved food and beverages placed in a paper based breakfast bag.</p>
				<p>Bright Sparqe secondary objectives are to increase the community's awareness on the homelessness issue by increasing exposure and focusing on the homeless getting a good start to the day. Bright Sparqe will provide information on other homeless support services available to help them back into the community</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
